import pandas as pd
import cufflinks
cufflinks.go_offline()

data_h5 = "../data/data.h5"

title = "24g/PM10"
all_data = pd.read_hdf(data_h5, title)
metadata = pd.read_hdf(data_h5, "metadata")

cols = all_data.columns.str.startswith("MpKra")
all_data.iloc[:,cols].iplot(yTitle="g/m3", title=title)

all_data.iloc[:,cols].groupby(pd.Grouper(freq="M")).mean().iplot(yTitle="g/m3", title=f"{title} averaged out over each month.")

Map of stations¶

from bokeh.io import show, output_notebook
from bokeh.plotting import figure
from bokeh.tile_providers import get_provider
from bokeh.models import HoverTool, PanTool, WheelZoomTool
from bokeh.models import ColumnDataSource

output_notebook()

E_minmax = metadata['web_mercator_E'].min(), metadata['web_mercator_E'].max()
N_minmax = metadata['web_mercator_N'].min(), metadata['web_mercator_N'].max()

source = ColumnDataSource(metadata)

hover = HoverTool(
        tooltips=[
            ("Stacja", "@{Nazwa stacji}")
        ]
    )

fig = figure(
    tools=[hover, PanTool(), WheelZoomTool()],
    x_range=E_minmax,
    y_range=N_minmax,
    x_axis_type="mercator",
    y_axis_type="mercator")
fig.add_tile(get_provider('CARTODBPOSITRON_RETINA'))
fig.circle(
    x='web_mercator_E',
    y='web_mercator_N',
    source=ColumnDataSource(metadata),
    line_color='grey',
    fill_color='yellow')

show(fig)
